   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 3 of our lords Gallus and Volusianus, Augusti, Hathyr 7. Aurelius Heron and Aurelius Kopres, both former agoranomoi, have paid, in the name of Pleein, son of Mysthes, 3 artabai of wheat(?) and 1/2 (art.) of barley, and lentils, in full. I, Aurelius Serenus, have signed.</ab>
